# Power BI User Guide

## Introduction
Welcome to the Power BI User Guide. This guide will help you get started with Power BI and make the most of its features.

## Getting Started
- Creating an account
- Setting up your first dashboard
- Connecting to data sources

## Basic Features
- Creating visualizations
- Using filters and slicers
- Sharing dashboards

## Advanced Features
- Using Power BI Desktop
- Advanced data transformations
- Custom visuals
